message.content: The paper likely belongs to the arXiv CS sub-category "cs.CL" (Computation and Language), as it deals with natural language processing and question generation. Other possible sub-categories could include "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence), "cs.LG" (Machine Learning), "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval), and "cs.DB" (Databases), as these fields are also relevant to the topic of knowledge base triples and question generation. However, "cs.CL" is the most likely sub-category given the focus on natural language processing.
